<plot>It is a true story, and was casted with the same disabled people on which the story had been based. The Making of followed it from inception to completion, observing the screenplay and casting process, the preparation of costumes and set design, shooting, Avid post-production, film printing and development in laboratories with the director of photography, audio mixing and dubbing, all the way until it was presented in the Turin Film Festival and then distributed in cinemas.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?353753</url></doc>
